description:
Darren is just fucking adorable!

He's got a cute, innocent face and a tight swimmer's body.

He was friendly and outgoing from the moment we met him and he was just super excited to be in California.

"I'm from the east coast," he said. "It's freezing there right now."

We took him out to see the sun set over the Pacific Ocean. He was like a kid in a candy store... he thought it was the neatest thing he'd ever seen!
title: Darren
